Package photos.model

Class Album

java.lang.Object
photos.model.Album
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Album extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a photo album containing multiple photos. Each album has a unique name and tracks the date range of its photos. Albums maintain references to Photo objects, allowing photos to exist in multiple albums.
Author:
Keegan Tu
